prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D comic book style greeting card front. A dynamic and hilarious action scene where Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are transformed into comic book superheroes. Lao Lao, in her light blue sweatshirt, is "Super Lao Lao," striking a heroic, confident pose front and center. She has a wide, joyful smile and one hand on her hip, while the other hand holds up a giant, steaming, magical coffee mug that radiates energy lines. Jordan, in his brown hoodie, is her trusty sidekick, standing slightly behind her with a comically amazed expression, pointing towards her as if presenting her greatness. They are surrounded by a team of adorable, small "super-dogs" of various cute breeds, each wearing a tiny hero cape and mask, leaping and flying through the air around the couple in action poses. The background is a vibrant city skyline bursting with color, featuring classic comic book "POW!" and "ZAP!" sound effect bubbles. In the center of the card, floating in a dynamic, fun-to-read comic book font, is the text "Happy Birthday to My Super Lao Lao!". The overall illustration uses bold outlines, a vibrant color palette with lots of primary colors, and halftone dot patterns for shading, creating an authentic, retro comic book feel.
